data.description: FABULOUS!!!! Move in and sit down. Shouts PRIDE of ownership. Property is improved.  The block glass allows for plenty of sunlight. Amenities includes: Enclosed porch, hardwood, ceramic tile flooring, modern kitchen,  2 full bathrooms  - 1 bathroom is in the basement  The basement is finished .  One off street parking spot in the rear with rear entrance.  House is conveniently located near City Avenue and public transportation.  This residence is 10 blocks from Saint Josephs University and 5 minutes by public transportation from local shopping center and the Mann Music Center. Seller is selling this well kept property As-Is. If you want a home that brags love and care, this is it!!
